snippet.title: Genetic Disaster Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam store page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/672460/Genetic_Disaster/

Genetic Disaster is a coop action game based around absurd guns, crazy characters and instant fun with procedurally generated levels for endless hours of accidental friendly fire in multiplayer!

Watch out for the madness everywhere:
→ Website: http://www.genetic-disaster.com/
→ Our Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/geneticdisaster
→ Our Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team8_Studio
